litter %>%
  mutate(Year = year(Date_collected)) %>%
  group_by(Plot, Year) %>%
  summarize(All_Leaf_annual = sum(All_Leaf,na.rm = TRUE)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(Year)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(Year, All_Leaf_annual, color = Plot)) + geom_line()
`summarise()` has grouped output by 'Plot'. You can override using the `.groups` argument.
